thread.title: Mystery $560 million Powerball winner finally claims her prize

title: Mystery $560 million Powerball winner finally claims her prize
text:
Mystery $560 million Powerball winner finally claims her prize Thursday, March 08, 2018 - 00:49 
The winner of a $560 million Powerball jackpot, who sued the New Hampshire state lottery commission to remain anonymous, has collected her prize and is keeping her privacy...for now. Linda So reports.
